title: Royalty and stars attend BAFTA awards
text: Royalty and stars attend BAFTA awards Catherine, Duchess of Cambridge and Prince William, Duke of Cambridge attend the 70th EE British Academy Film Awards (BAFTA) at Royal Albert Hall on Feb. 12, 2017 in London.
